30/*
31 * This header file contains mode setting related functions and definitions
32 * which are only used within the drm module as internal implementation details
33 * and are not exported to drivers.
34 */
35
36int drm_mode_object_get(struct drm_device *dev,
37 struct drm_mode_object *obj, uint32_t obj_type);
38void drm_mode_object_put(struct drm_device *dev,
39 struct drm_mode_object *object);
40
41/* drm_atomic.c */

43 struct drm_property *property, uint64_t *val);
44int drm_mode_atomic_ioctl(struct drm_device *dev,
45 void *data, struct drm_file *file_priv);
